Try to write the requirements for simple arcade style driving game where the player has to navigate around obstacles to keep from crashing.
Player MUST be able to accelerate.
Player MUST be able to decelerate.
Player MUST be able to turn/navigate the car. 
Obstacles should MUST render in time for the player to be able to have an appropriate response time. 
Player's score must be kept.
Player's score must restart when they crash. 


Try to write the requirements for a program that bounces a ball off the sides of the screen and any obstacles larger than 3 pixels the user draws with the mouse.
User must be able to draw on screen.
The ball must move.
The user must be able to erase what they have drawn.
